high_descs: Move to the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the sink.
Bring the knife to the coffee machine.
Put the knife in the mug on the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it in the sink.

high_descs: walk over to the kitchen sink
grab the knife off the kitchen counter to the left of the sink
back up and move to the right to face the coffee maker
place the knife inside of the cup under the coffee maker
pick up the cup under the coffee maker
back up a bit and move over to face the sink on the left
place the cup inside of the sink
anns.task_desc: get a cup with a knife in it inside the sink

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the sink.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife that is in front of the sponge to the left of the sink.
Carry the knife to the coffee maker to the right of the sink.
Put the knife, handle-first, into the cup on the coffee maker.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Go back to the sink to your left.
Place the cup holding the knife into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup holding a knife into the kitchen sink.
